Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.59,0:00:04.42,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,受到东南亚金融危机的影响  股价暴跌之后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.52,0:00:07.16,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然股票市场看来暂时有所回复
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:11.90,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,但有人随机向全国银行账户汇入数万亿日元  引起了骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.95,0:00:14.45,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,同时物价的急剧上升导致日元市价…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:16.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,一美元换三千日元?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:18.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓了  快给我兑换啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:21.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,有些店只用美元卖东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.67,0:00:25.22,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,This movement of the Yen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.67,0:00:25.22,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,这次日元的动荡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.22,0:00:27.18,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,is irrelevant to {\i1}C{\r}, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.22,0:00:27.18,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,和「C」没有关系吧  是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.47,0:00:28.05,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.47,0:00:28.05,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:30.14,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,It is sort of conspiracy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:30.14,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,那是由于某种阴谋而导致的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.05,0:00:31.93,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,What about 「C」?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.05,0:00:31.93,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,那「C」的情况如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:33.27,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:33.27,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,请看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.13,0:00:46.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.70,0:00:50.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个世间的人还真是单纯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.94,0:00:56.13,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道总有一天事情会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.56,0:00:57.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这么想的  Q
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.57,0:00:59.69,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,这是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.18,0:01:01.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不  这是必然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.07,0:01:04.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我总感觉只是一场必须获胜的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.45,0:01:07.54,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.57,0:01:08.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,或许如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:10.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:11.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:14.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,到结算还有一小时的时间


Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:03.24,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Open Deal」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:04.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,公主!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:06.41,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Sleeping Beauty Micro Flation」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:09.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真朱  Micro Flation  五千万
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:18.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,十亿!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:18.82,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Direct」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:23.67,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Direct」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.23,0:03:24.96,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Direct」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:26.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,公麿!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:37.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真朱  回来!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.52,0:03:39.06,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Trade」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:41.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mezzo Flation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:42.53,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「EBO」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:44.65,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Direct」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你说不能兑换了  是怎么回事?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:57.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,各国已经停止使用日元交易
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:04.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,全世界最坚挺的货币化为废纸  没想到真有这么一天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:07.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,必须要做好觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:10.40,Mask,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1217,181)}远东金融街的下场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:17.60,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Direct」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:18.85,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Direct」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.15,0:04:27.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:31.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Q!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.57,0:04:35.37,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Macro… Mezzo… Micro」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:40.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,杰鲁杰!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.17,0:04:47.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真危险  真危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:48.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,那边也糟糕的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.09,0:04:50.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,这边也会糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:51.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真是糟糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:58.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾  我还希望你能继承我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.35,0:05:03.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,无论发生什么我都希望这一刻能成为永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:06.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾坚信着我们能同享这一价值观
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:08.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:11.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,只是看法不同罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:12.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,目的是相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:16.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,只是时机已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:18.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,公麿  只能用Macro了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:23.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想… 用Macro出击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:26.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,全力… 我想全力应战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:29.22,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Micro Mezzo Macro Flation」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.67,0:05:30.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Q
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:32.47,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Economic Blockade」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:33.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真朱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:35.10,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Overheated Economy」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:43.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不能动了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:48.99,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,受金融厅的命令在全国实行的禁止外币兑换措施
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:51.78,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,导致各地情况几近于暴乱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:55.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有妹妹  也遭遇了相同的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:55.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:58.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定会赞同我的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:00.00,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Direct」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,令妹真的希望这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:06.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你只是为了自己而这么做不是吗?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:09.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么是为了现在  为了弱者而行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:11.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,结果  不都是为了一己之利吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.59,0:06:14.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,少自以为是!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:18.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:21.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你说不是美元就不能购买是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:21.19,Mask,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1217,157)}首都内某处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:23.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,那不只是谣言而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:26.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,或许是谣言  但这是总店的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不能收取日元出售货品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:34.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,能动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.61,0:06:36.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真朱  Charge!10亿!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:37.93,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Micro Mezzo Flation」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:38.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:42.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:45.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说我们Asset就是Entre的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:48.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要为了公麿而战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:53.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,但是公麿却在为了我而战斗  这样不是很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:55.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:57.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,才没有这么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:59.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我却觉得  这样反而能让我感到安心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:00.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:03.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,最后一次和妹妹对话的时候  妹妹这么说道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:05.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,「如果今天能一直延续就好了」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:09.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,「像这样毫无改变的每一天能够永远持续就好了」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:14.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,无法感受明日的妹妹  这是镌刻在她血肉之中的呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:15.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你能理解吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:18.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以说「现在对我来说最重要」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.99,0:07:23.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,子欲养而亲不在  人本来就应该珍视怜惜眼前的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:28.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,而不应杞人忧天  去为难以捉摸的未来操心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:32.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  异变就在我眼前发生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:33.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:38.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要珍惜身边的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:42.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不暗中操作  一切都会崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:46.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的行动能让人获救
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:47.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,倘若再没有未来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:52.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,即使被拯救又有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:57.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹真正想说的是「不对」不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:08:00.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,对你自己所说过的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:05.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,看了首相的会面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,政府也真是使出了吃奶的劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:11.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能会有人相信政府所说的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:12.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你会离开日本吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:15.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,聪明的家伙已经离开日本了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:18.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,三国先生说他有个妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:20.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,已经不能再醒来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:22.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:24.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Scorched Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:32.15,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Cannibalization」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:35.74,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Micro Mezzo Macro Flation」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:35.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Scorched…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:36.74,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Economic Blockade」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:40.99,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Cannibalization」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:42.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.49,0:08:46.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  你和她妹妹一摸一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:48.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:51.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不是妹妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:53.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,三国先生正在做的事是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:57.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,吸取你的血来给「你」输血
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:08:58.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,区区Asset敢对我说教?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:04.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,和他相遇真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:05.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,还敢继续说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.43,0:09:08.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然讨厌和他分离
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:10.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我也会这么战斗着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:12.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,为了他而战斗着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:14.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你为了什么而战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:16.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,是为了三国先生而战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:17.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,那三国先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:19.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是为了你而战吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:20.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.57,0:09:22.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴  闭嘴!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:32.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  找的零钱里头有玩具钱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:33.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:37.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我在问你这漆黑的钱是什么东西啊

Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:53.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,无论我怎么做  无论你怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:56.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,人类早晚都会毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:10:00.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,所以  每天我都当成人生的最后一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:01.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,拼尽全力活下去!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:02.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,明天会是怎么样都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.86,0:10:05.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已  仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:08.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果明天比昨天还要悲惨  那怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:10.40,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Direct」!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:12.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样明天依然会到来!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:19.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Q  吃掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:21.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉这个Entre
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:23.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Q
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:28.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,贵子…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.01,0:10:30.55,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Direct」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:31.72,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「Direct」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:42.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,梦醒的时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:03.46,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,C's chain reaction is about to hit Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:03.46,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,「C」连锁到达日本了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.55,0:11:09.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:13.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,三国壮一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:24.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:28.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,只是有点累了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:30.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下也好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:32.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥已经战斗的足够多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:33.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,贵子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:36.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥最近很像爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:40.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也有想要守护的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:42.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是和哥哥一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:44.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,很像爸爸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:47.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…说不定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:54.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样  那至今为止我做的那些又算是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.28,0:11:56.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,贵子?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:59.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,贵子  贵子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:09.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,贵子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:27.50,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The chain action passed though Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:27.50,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,「C」连锁已经通过了日本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:29.67,IMF_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,How in the world can that be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:29.67,IMF,,0000,0000,0000,,…怎么可能这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:37.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,日元失去价值的话  Midas Money也就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:41.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,于是「C」的连锁好像已经通过日本了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:43.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个远东金融街迟早会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.52,0:12:48.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你们还在Deal中呢  这可如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:50.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,是我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:52.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:55.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,三国先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:58.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:03.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,给我反转印钞机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:06.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不会后悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:11.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,那做你所想做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.80,0:13:15.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,谨遵…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:21.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要把未来买回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:24.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,尊意!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.09,Asset,,0000,0000,0000,,「You have control」\N您获得控制权
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:12.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,看来要分别了  Q
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:18.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  今后不再为你而战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:21.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,去本该去的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:25.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果还能在你的身边就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:27.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:29.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊  Q
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:33.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不对  贵子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:41.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,赢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:47.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:49.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:52.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,该不会说… 要分别?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:57.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,三十倍…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:14:59.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你说过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:32.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我觉得  差不多是平时的四十倍那样喜欢着你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:34.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真朱…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:40.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,遇见你  真好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:43.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真朱… 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:01.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:03.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在未来相见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:10.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我要永远停留在这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:25.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.89,0:16:36.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我认为无论什么事  信用都是第一位的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:40.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,但没想到金融街的信用这么简单就失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:43.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要小心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:46.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道什么时候会发生什么样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:48.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,好像已经晚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:56.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你对金融街的依赖看来是比想象中更厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:00.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,还是逃不掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.02,0:17:04.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,这不正说明你备受信任吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:20.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,看来是不能再偏袒你的任性了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:37.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:40.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,对于什么是正确的  什么是错误
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:42.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你很迷茫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:44.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,没有正确的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:45.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:48.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是为了让世界变得更美好而战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:51.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,而且世界的确变得更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:53.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,那么  金融街是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:57.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,正是因为有了它  你们才会相遇  战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.94,0:17:59.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,世间万物皆有其存在意义
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:03.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,无论它有多邪恶东西  无论它有多悲惨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:07.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,必定都有把人类引向更好道路上的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:10.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要看到这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:11.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:15.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你要回去的世界已经完全变了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:18.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你  还有你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:21.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,得回了非常重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:21.02,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,（背景为复利公式。）
Comment: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:27.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,----Epilogue
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:23.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.73,0:20:10.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,球跑到那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:35.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,一共是七美元三十美分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:39.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,七美元三十美分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:40.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,正好不用找
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:52.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,快点  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:54.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:55.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:56.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,跑起来比较危险哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:20:58.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:08.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,健治小朋友  不能插队哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.15,0:21:14.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  大家有没有好好跟着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:17.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,羽奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:18.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:21.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看  狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:24.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,狗狗? 好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:38.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,看到与曾经喜欢的女生极为相像的保育员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:43.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,「说不定她也在某个地方得回了幸福未来吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:46.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你正沉浸在这样的感慨中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:48.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,打扰你实在是过意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:50.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.51,0:21:52.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不是  不是骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:54.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你还在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.63,0:21:56.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你取回来的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:22:00.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,对我们来说  未来便是抵押
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:04.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,未来存在的地方  我也一样存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.85,0:22:07.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,金融街是不会毁灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:09.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.99,0:22:10.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:17.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,可以用于抵押的未来比起原来可是多得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.13,0:22:20.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有这个意愿的话  可以随时叫我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.29,0:22:22.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,那我告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:47.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,当时有笑一笑就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.71,0:22:50.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,…向着那未来

Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,----ED
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:54.47,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄从窗子逃出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.14,0:18:57.72,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚的街市
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.77,0:19:01.31,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,化为RPG游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.48,0:19:05.73,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,沿着箭头的方向  我被带入
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:08.73,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,一个五光十色的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:12.03,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,响起开始的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:17.03,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,全身为爱煎熬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:20.00,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,想要见到你和你的未来  我披荆斩棘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:23.16,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,穿越黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:26.92,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,高潮什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:29.63,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,就算来不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:34.01,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,就算必须乾坤一掷  也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:35.47,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,让我爱上你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:40.64,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要迷上你  还有你的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:43.73,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,即使欺骗全世界也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.90,0:19:46.52,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,现在就拉起我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:48.82,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是AB选择
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:51.48,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,也不能用道理说清
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:54.45,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,比起全世界的未解之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:20:04.83,EDC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,2000)}我更想知道你的未来  你的心

